{"tid":876164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為種榴槤供華　大馬焚林趕絕馬來虎","createTime":"2018-10-25T12:16:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T03:26:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8142f533dd2b4f7113a02d7b603be015117eb176","tid":876164,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T12:16:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181025/20530135\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181025%2F20530135&d=fgFrnIcvcWuwYkN8wU6h4TPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=6b3cefe5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181025%2F20530135&h=9cafb35d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181025/20530135</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月25日 <br />\n<br />\n為種榴槤供華　大馬焚林趕絕馬來虎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181025/large/25wx08p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181025%2Flarge%2F25wx08p.jpg&h=d7779642&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現時全球馬來虎數目不足300隻。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞為迎合中國榴槤熱，將彭亨州勞勿縣1,213公頃的森林燒毀和鏟平，趕絕稀有的馬來虎。該處將由與政府有關的公司種植貓山王。彭亨州林業部證實在該範圍鏟林毋須得到該部門許可。世界自然基金會批評，行動對馬來虎的存活造成致命的傷害。<br />\n<br />\n馬來虎全球僅剩不足300隻，是極危物種。世界自然基金會大馬幹事阿比丁指，馬來虎絕無僅有，只活躍於馬來半島和泰國南部，被燒毀的森林鄰近馬來虎的主要棲息地，「燒毀該片森林將使整個森林變得支離破碎，嚴重影響野生生態」。<br />\n<br />\n勞勿縣的森林近年變成中國旅客尋覓榴槤的熱點。過去十年，中國的榴槤進口量平均每年攀升26%，前年達11億美元（約85.8億港元）。榴槤熱已使馬來西亞去年的榴槤價格飛升，果農大規模種植榴槤。市場預料，榴槤將取代棕櫚油，成為馬來西亞出口量最高的產品。<br />\n<br />\n英國《衞報》  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n意拒削赤　歐盟首駁回成員國預算案<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n索羅斯、奧巴馬、希拉莉收炸彈郵包"},{"pid":"92f19b1906fee6559307338ef3775a15e5b5727a","tid":876164,"uid":51546,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T12:17:52.000Z","msg":"人類真係世界毒瘤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2627affe1117d619536c840945488e8b323faee","tid":876164,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T12:18:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f83330aedcf08cb8d64cd2439770adb74f8bee90","tid":876164,"uid":40478,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"92f19b1906fee6559307338ef3775a15e5b5727a","tid":876164,"uid":51546,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T12:17:52.000Z","msg":"人類真係世界毒瘤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T12:18:50.000Z","msg":"中國人係世界毒瘤"},{"pid":"76cbce419cae866000f9a00d7af42505b9bc0874","tid":876164,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"f83330aedcf08cb8d64cd2439770adb74f8bee90","tid":876164,"uid":40478,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"92f19b1906fee6559307338ef3775a15e5b5727a","tid":876164,"uid":51546,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T12:17:52.000Z","msg":"人類真係世界毒瘤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T12:18:50.000Z","msg":"中國人係世界毒瘤"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T12:19:09.000Z","msg":"中國人唔係人？"},{"pid":"05a33ad06ddcfe956d5c4ad756e649d6fa5b932d","tid":876164,"uid":82532,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T12:20:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/25/82/f1/2582f132fca30507b99c9313029bdb6d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F25%2F82%2Ff1%2F2582f132fca30507b99c9313029bdb6d.jpg&h=dd328ad2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"876b8a362b7794dca6cff9f7be6b6540cef694cd","tid":876164,"uid":99700